rows.label: tlk41300012_01_msg0001
rows.name:
There's this legendary merc
a pal of mine told me about,
Zoquim.

rows.label: tlk41300012_01_msg0002
rows.name:
And get this: he's got a huge sweet
tooth. Can't say no to a Cinnopon Roll.

rows.label: tlk41300012_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Just one Cinnopon Roll and he'll
be pumped for the next battle.

rows.label: tlk41300012_01_msg0004
rows.name:
It's similar to how my wife's got a
serious thing for Eau de Doux.

rows.label: tlk41300012_01_msg0005
rows.name:
Pleasant smells are conducive to a
good working environment, she says.

rows.label: tlk41300012_01_msg0006
rows.name:
You should find that special something
that peps you up as well.
